</head>And they&#8217;re back! On Saturday, 1 April, cricket teams and supporters will gather to take part and cheer on in the annual Winter T20 League. The Winter T20 league sees a number of local players coming together to battle it out on the field. This year matches will be held at various grounds throughout Durban.Toti Field (Hutchison Park), Amanzimtoti Sports Facility Lahee Park, 25 Anderson Road Pinetown Lutherfield, Kloof Country Club, Kloof Asherville Sports Field, Tarndale Avenue, Off Rd Naidu Drive Kingsmead Oval GroundResidents are welcome to attend and show support for their favourite teams. Bring along your picnic basket and camp chair! 01.04.2017 Saturday Afternoon